Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================APART========================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正继续旅行德我们一行人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特务搜查官维瑟突然再次出现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是绑架宠物？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要什么都算到我头上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全都怪那普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我绝对要抓住那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底洗清我的嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drifter 追或是被追！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野猪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炎球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.41,0:02:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里 你那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是狼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今只能放手一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 再怎么说这也太过分了吧 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再怎么想抓住普库塔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫它先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 也不要把无辜的动物们卷入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哦 如果我真拿出野性本能来知道会怎样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从追踪普库塔进了森林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口的全是人畜无害的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要的是动物性蛋白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继盗贼之后 你想让全世界的动物都灭绝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直持续这种没计划又没效率的事 根本没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没办法一次性解决吗 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真会说 自己明明就是个甩手掌柜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想快点解决的话你也稍微帮下忙啊 杰路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子还是那么严肃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下你后悔我也不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说后悔？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过那小动物虽然嚣张 却会使用龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能造出光之剑的复制品和破坏魔导战车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不想承认 但它确实不是泛泛之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在想 搞不好他也知道杰路想要的情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这只不过是我个人的猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会这么巧就正好知道能将\N变成合成兽的身体变回原样的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有想拦你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰路就请先下山去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 快走快走 请请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍这种一眼就看穿的花招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说她还真以为我会经不住挑拨如她所愿么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要被人如此看轻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使山顶的湖决堤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能将森林里的野兽一口气冲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振动弹…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你想什么呢杰路刚帝士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底什么意思啊莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就可以放心进行别的作战计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的作战计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 我也一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这里交给他们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点出发吧 高里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振动…弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的作战计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好主意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你偶尔也给我动动…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动动…脑筋？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 就把我珍藏的作战计划告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我亲手抓住你 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全变了一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰路刚帝士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不再破坏森林了倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是会中这种原始陷阱的人根本不存在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对象是莉娜和高里的话就很难说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算是他们俩 这种诱饵也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 莉娜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是能使用和莉娜同等攻击魔法的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 当然他也要消耗和莉娜等量的卡路里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到他也必须补充这部分的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易想象他会和莉娜高里他们一样暴饮暴食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 得出的答案只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你别那么认真考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是这种意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 是那女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.76,0:08:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想 想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子知道让我的身体恢复原样的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道才有鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:09:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 这样还想说不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 想动手？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也应该知道我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早料到会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在诱饵中混入了麻醉药
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰 杰路刚帝士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种像反派般的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 老实交代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错你了 杰路刚帝士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道什么叫手下留情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有杰路刚帝士和莉娜没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来给你解毒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 阿梅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反目成仇根本不能解决任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰路刚帝士你为什么就不能更冷静一点来交流呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这种家伙没什么好交流的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义是建立在理解之上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在该做的是坦率地敞开心扉 相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 普库塔到底为什么要让莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上破坏魔导战车的黑锅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背黑锅？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不关我事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人被怀疑 纯粹是因为她平时作风不正吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 说到底普库塔为什么想要去破坏魔导战车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着那种危险的东西不管 岂不是太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在偷魔导战车的人拿它去干坏事之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先把它破坏掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干坏事之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了世界和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是正义 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别尽说些好听的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么偷魔导战车的到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到底在计划什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这…不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我必须尽快破坏掉所有的魔导战车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没闲工夫在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨磨蹭蹭了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去行使正义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将魔导战车找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越一直以来的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被伟大的爱与正义的力量结合在一起的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨过天际 冲向魔导战车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后终将维护世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都将从今天这一步开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 何等美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人心中涌起一股暖流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山川啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请聆听我阿梅莉娜正义的呐喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 几时爬到那种地方去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}{\an8}（хорошо：俄语“棒极了”之意）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情好好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 打起精神前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索魔导战车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用 尽管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足满足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 这也是为了世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说的好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空腹无以扬正义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 下一份还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是自我感觉良好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧这一脸放松的睡相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说明他有这么信赖我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么总感觉是被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是魔导战车啊 魔导战车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往正义之心指引了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔导战车 在这里碰上我算你倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算是魔导战车？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快速度 速度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说还真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到我们居然会去制作冒牌的魔导战车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为把普库塔引出来的话 用不着真货吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要外表像就行了 外表像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里像了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿梅莉亚也在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Mono Volt{\r}\N雷击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说阿梅莉亚 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招 炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此那这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Val-Flare{\r}\N爆炎矢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封气结界咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防御结界？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 真是疲软
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}　　　　　　　　Vice Flare{\r}\N既然如此就上炎裂炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 这可不是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个正义宅王女…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢如此对待凝聚我心血的可爱小雪兔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪兔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此我要开始反击了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里 右舷炮塔30度展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向左40度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才被你们打得好惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢反击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢 炎之矢 炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方向盘有意义吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦 玩的就是气氛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个魔导战车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏接下来才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炎球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Freeze Brid{\r}\N冰结弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为拼魔法可以赢我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Bomb Di Wind{\r}\N风魔咆裂弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Burst Flare{\r}\N看招吧 裂火球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 冷静点 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一招定胜负 跟我来阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呸呸大蠢货 小软蛋 下仁田的葱头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普库塔那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里 向右40度旋回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还是向左
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 向右60度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了 阿梅莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Arc Brass{\r}\N地灵咆雷阵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和普库塔第一次的协同作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是正义与友情的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚 这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你几时变成小动物的手下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷魔导战车要去干坏事的 就是莉娜你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错你了 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会变成那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌货啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场闹剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌货？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白忙一场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 普库塔你给我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来和我堂堂正正分胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁还要继续待在这里陪你玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听吗 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始也为时不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到维瑟先生那去自首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样至少罪行会轻一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是该听我解释啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些就别提了 我们的村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维瑟负责修理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 普库塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 话说高里在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关我鸟事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================ED========================
